 《美国恐怖故事》主演加文·克里尔去世，享年 48 岁https://www.nme.com/news/tv/american-horror-stories-star-gavin-creel-dies-ged-48-3798600?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=american-horror-stories-star-gavin-鱼架死亡 48 岁Max PilleyTue, 01 Oct 2024 10:30:43 +0000 NewsTV News.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3798600 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他还因其在百老汇和西区舞台上的职业生涯而获得托尼奖和奥利弗奖</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/american-horror-stories-star-gavin-creel-dies-aged-48-3798600">《美国恐怖故事》后的主演加文·克里尔去世，享年 48 岁，</a>首次出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/gavin_creel_rip-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>百老汇和西区舞台音乐剧以及<i>《美国恐怖故事》</i>的明星加文·克里尔去世，享年 48 岁。</p><p>这位托尼奖得主演员于 7 月被诊断出患有一种罕见的癌症，他的伴侣亚历克斯·坦普尔·沃德 (Alex Temple Ward) 于周一（9 月 30 日）证实了他去世的消息。</p><p>他患有转移性黑色素周围神经鞘肉瘤，在纪念斯隆·凯特琳医院接受治疗，最近转为在家接受临终关怀。他在曼哈顿的家中去世。</p><p>克里尔凭借<i>《你好，多莉！》</i>中的角色获得了托尼音乐剧最佳男配角奖。 2017 年，他在百老汇与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bette-midler">贝蒂·米勒 (Bette Midler)</a>和大卫·海德·皮尔斯 (David Hyde Pierce) 演对手戏。此前，他曾因<i>《彻底现代的米莉》(Thoroughly Modern Millie)</i>和<i>《头发》(Hair)</i>中的角色获得提名。</p><p>得知这一消息后，米德勒在 Instagram 上写道，她“期待每晚与他一起工作”。她补充道：“他太棒了。我不敢相信他已经走了。真是损失惨重啊。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DAjWXfly87_/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.5